{"tid":272651,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一部你最中意嘅港產片","createTime":"2017-06-06T03:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T09:59:51.000Z","uid":84931,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e03114f3fbdda49685c22cd8542077c4ae9b0d8","tid":272651,"uid":84931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T03:56:18.000Z","msg":"是咁的 呢排想做份artwork 主題係關於香港電影 大概嘅方向會係一部份嘅影評再加一幅插畫 <br />\n<br />\n有幾套都諗住開始構思點畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n踏血尋梅 - 援交/ 因寂寞而利用性去尋找救贖<br />\n早熟  - 香港人嘅理想與現實<br />\n老笠 - 社會上嘅毛病/ 反映香港都市壓力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">求各位ching幫吓手諗下有咩港產片你睇完係好撚有共嗚 更係令你有反思到呢套戲同香港嘅現況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> [/size=4]</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申<br />\n我知大家會當我9up  但係幫吓手諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d034fde72de7b5e15c9bd6788c54bae4717963b","tid":272651,"uid":44461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T04:05:29.000Z","msg":"個標題有啲問題，應該係「一人一套你鐘意又可以反映到香港現況嘅港產片」<br />\n如果唔係我實答王家衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw一念無明"},{"pid":"080229fa89dee24ea4f285523a2101fd6d538652","tid":272651,"uid":84931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T04:09:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個標題有啲問題，應該係「一人一套你鐘意又可以反映到香港現況嘅港產片」<br />\n如果唔係我實答王家衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw一念無明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我仲未睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打有無link"},{"pid":"ab6ac091500224680a3362815ebd3973d39a2452","tid":272651,"uid":120051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T04:15:04.000Z","msg":"五個小孩的校長"},{"pid":"b647f5d01bbd982048846511cfc3a572e1696dbc","tid":272651,"uid":113456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T04:19:29.000Z","msg":"好似唔關事 但好中意 妄想同怪物"},{"pid":"9250a59c6665e0bb4ba24b651dff542984